│   └── ...
├── Consciousness/                  # If consciousness enabled
├── External/                       # URL/Package references
└── Workspaces/                     # User projects

**Implementation note**: This hierarchy is **logical**, built from `parent_id` + optional `materialized_path`. Every item is a **Container** (not a separate folder).

